WEBVTT

NOTE: Estimated from known TTS script; timing requires human review before Tier 1 captions.

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.314
If you need to sell your house fast in Green Bay, Wisconsin, USA Home Buyers can make you a direct cash offer and buy the property as-is.

2
00:00:10.314 --> 00:00:19.482
We work with homeowners across Green Bay and Brown County, including Astor Park, Fort Howard, Downtown Green Bay, and the broader Green Bay area.

3
00:00:19.482 --> 00:00:23.302
Some Green Bay homes are not a simple retail listing.

4
00:00:23.302 --> 00:00:31.324
The house may be inherited, vacant, tenant-occupied, near the stadium area, older, or carrying repairs you do not want to manage.

5
00:00:31.324 --> 00:00:41.256
You do not have to fix the roof, clean out the basement, update old systems, or wait for a buyer to ask for credits after inspection.

6
00:00:41.256 --> 00:00:43.756
Here is how it works.

7
00:00:43.756 --> 00:00:47.576
You tell us about the property and your preferred timeline.

8
00:00:47.576 --> 00:00:52.924
We review the home, answer your questions, and give you a written cash offer.

9
00:00:52.924 --> 00:00:55.980
