10
00:00:55.980 --> 00:01:01.710
If you need time for family, moving, or probate details, we can discuss that upfront.

11
00:01:01.710 --> 00:01:04.767
There are no agent commissions and no obligation.

12
00:01:04.767 --> 00:01:11.261
We explain the offer in plain English so you know what to expect before making a decision.

13
00:01:11.261 --> 00:01:17.373
For a no-pressure cash offer on a Green Bay-area house, call USA Home Buyers at 888-274-5006.

14
00:01:17.373 --> 00:01:21.367
We will help you decide whether selling as-is is the right move.
